resources.string: The application will help you load your processor to the maximum and help you find out how productive it is.\n\nWorking principle: when the test starts, a secondary thread is launched, in which it counts the points in an infinite order. Then it all depends on your processor, the faster it can process a lot of data from a secondary thread, the more points you will get
During the test, do not turn off the device and do not exit app, as this may result in inaccurate results.\n\nTest time: 01:00
